---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section
  class="dotted-overlay flex min-h-screen flex-col justify-center bg-black after:absolute after:inset-0 after:bg-black/30"
>
  <picture>
    <source srcset="/images/idiomas/hero.webp" type="image/webp" />
    <source srcset="/images/idiomas/hero.avif" type="image/avif" />
    <img
      class="absolute inset-0 mx-auto h-screen w-full object-cover object-bottom"
      src="/images/idiomas/hero.webp"
    />
  </picture>

  <div class="relative z-10 container flex justify-center text-center">
    <div
      class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center space-y-4 text-center"
    >
      <h1
        class="animate-blurred-fade-in text-heading-1 gap-1 leading-none font-black text-white"
      >
        Aprender idiomas en el extranjero es vivir una
        <b class="text-cteal-100">experiencia que te transforma</b>
      </h1>
      <p
        class="animate-blurred-fade-in animate-delay-100 max-w-4xl text-xs text-white min-sm:block sm:text-sm md:text-base min-lg:text-2xl"
      >
        Estudia en destinos incre√≠bles, conoce personas de todo el mundo y
        potencia tu crecimiento personal y profesional. Haz que tu aprendizaje
        sea tan inolvidable como tu viaje
      </p>

      <a
        href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=573183795288&text=%C2%A1Hola!%20%C2%BFC%C3%B3mo%20est%C3%A1s%3F%20%F0%9F%98%84"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        target="_blank"
        class="bg-cpurple-200 hover:bg-cpurple-300 animate-blurred-fade-in animate-delay-150 mx-auto mt-5 mb-10 inline-block w-fit px-8 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition min-sm:text-base"
      >
        Hablemos ahora
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a
    role="button"
    href="#destinos"
    class="animate-bouncing animate-iteration-count-infinite absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 z-10 mx-auto hidden w-fit px-4 py-2 font-semibold lg:block lg:scale-110 2xl:scale-125"
    aria-label="Scroll down"
  >
    <Icon name="mouse" class="size-6 text-white lg:size-10" />
  </a>
</section>
